name: Pk.1comp.ke.Vd.difEq
equations:

Conc  <- Central / Vd

name: Pk.1comp.Cl.Vd.difEq
equations:
ke  <- Cl /Vd
dCentral <- -ke * Central
Conc  <- Central / Vd

name: Pk.1comp.ka.Cl.Vd.difEq
equations:
ke <- Cl/Vd
dGut <- - ka * Gut
dCentral <- -ke * Central + ka * Gut
Conc  <- Central / Vd

name: PD.Simeoni
equations:
growth <- lambda0 * X1 / (( 1 + ( lambda0 * tumVol / lambda1 ) ** psi ) ** ( 1 / psi ))
dtumVol <- tumVol *  growth

name: PD.Simeoni
equations:
tumVol <- X1 + X2 + X3 + X4
growth <- lambda0 * X1 /( ( 1 +( lambda0 * tumVol /lambda1)**psi)**(1/psi))
dX1 <- growth - X1 *  [PK] * k2
dX2 <- X1 * [PK] * k2 - k1 * X2
dX3 <- k1 * (X2 - X3)
dX4 <- k1 * (X3 - X4)

name: PD.Simeoni
equations:
tumVol <- X1 + X2 + X3 + X4
growth <- lambda0 * X1 /( ( (1 + lambda0 * tumVol/lambda1)**psi)**(1/psi))
effect <-  [PK1] * k2drug1 + [PK2] * k2drug2 +  [PK1] *  [PK2] * k2interac
dX1 <- growth - X1 * effect
dX2 <- X1 * effect - k1 * X2
dX3 <- k1* (X2 - X3)
dX4 <- k1 * (X3 - X4)

name: Pk.2comp.ke.k12.k21.difEq
equations:
#k12 <- Q/V1
#k21 <- Q/V2
#ke <- Cl/V1
dCentral <- k21 * Periph - k12 * Central - ke * Central
dPeriph <- - k21 * Periph + k12 * Central
Conc <- Central / V1

name: Pk.3comp.ke.k12.k21.difEq
equations:
dCentral <- k21 * Periph2 + k31 * Periph3 - Central * ( k12 + ke + k21 ) 
dPeriph2 <- - k21 * Periph2 + k12 * Central
dPeriph3 <- - k21 * Periph3 + k12 * Central
Conc <- Central / Vd

name: Pk.TMDD.full.1com
equations:
dL <- - ke * L - kon * L * R + koff * P
dR <-  ksyn - kdeg * R - kon * L * R + koff * P
dP <- kon * L * R - koff * P - kint * P
Conc <- L / Vd

name: Pk.TMDD.full.2com
equations:
dL <- - ke * L - kon * L * R + koff * P - k12 * L + k21 * A 
dR <-  ksyn - kdeg * R - kon * L * R + koff * P
dP <- kon * L * R - koff * P - kint * P
dA <-    k12 * L - k21 * A 
Conc <- L / Vd

name: Pk.TMDD.QE.1com
equations:
dLtot <- - kin * Ltot - (kel - kint) * L
dRtot <- ksyn - kdeg * Rtot - (kint - kdeg) * ( Ltot - L )
L <- 1 / 2 *  ( ( Ltot - Rtot - Kd ) + sqrt(( Ltot - Rtot - kd ) ** 2 + 4 * kd * Ltot ))
Conc <- L / Vd
